"código QR e instrucciones de pago."

#: includes/abstract-class-wc-gateway-paycrypto-me.php:194
msgid "Express Payment (One-Click)"
msgstr "Pago Exprés (Un Clic)"

#: includes/abstract-class-wc-gateway-paycrypto-me.php:195
msgid ""
"Enable Express Payment to pay with one click. When enabled, customers are "
"redirected straight to the payment QR code."
msgstr ""
"Habilita el Pago Exprés para pagar con un clic. Cuando está habilitado, los "
"clientes se redirigen directamente al código QR de pago."

#: includes/abstract-class-wc-gateway-paycrypto-me.php:198
msgid "Enable Express Payment"
msgstr "Habilitar Pago Exprés"

#: includes/abstract-class-wc-gateway-paycrypto-me.php:204
msgid "Express Button Label"
msgstr "Etiqueta del Botón Exprés"

#: includes/abstract-class-wc-gateway-paycrypto-me.php:205
#: includes/class-wc-gateway-paycrypto-me-lightning.php:42
#: includes/class-wc-gateway-paycrypto-me.php:47
msgid "Buy with"
msgstr "Comprar con"

#: includes/abstract-class-wc-gateway-paycrypto-me.php:206
msgid ""
"Text displayed on the Express Payment button. If empty, the default label "
"will be used 'Buy with'"
msgstr ""
"Texto que se muestra en el botón de Pago Exprés. Si está vacío, se usará la "
"etiqueta predeterminada 'Comprar con'"

#: includes/abstract-class-wc-gateway-paycrypto-me.php:213
msgid "Express Button Icon"
msgstr "Icono del Botón Exprés"

#: includes/abstract-class-wc-gateway-paycrypto-me.php:214
msgid "Show icon on Express Payment button"
msgstr "Mostrar icono en el botón de Pago Exprés"

#: includes/abstract-class-wc-gateway-paycrypto-me.php:217
msgid ""
"When enabled, the payment network icon is displayed alongside the button "
"label."
msgstr ""
"Cuando está habilitado, el icono de la red de pagos se muestra junto a la "
"etiqueta del botón."

#: includes/abstract-class-wc-gateway-paycrypto-me.php:220
msgid "Icon Position"
msgstr "Posición del Icono"

#: includes/abstract-class-wc-gateway-paycrypto-me.php:223
msgid ""
"Controls where the icon appears relative to the button label. e.g. \"₿ Pay "
"with\" (left) or \"Pay with ₿\" (right)."
msgstr ""
"Controla dónde aparece el icono en relación con la etiqueta del botón. Por "
"ejemplo, \"₿ Pagar con\" (izquierda) o \"Pagar con ₿\" (derecha)."

#: includes/abstract-class-wc-gateway-paycrypto-me.php:225
msgid "Left — icon before label"
msgstr "Izquierda — icono antes de la etiqueta"

#: includes/abstract-class-wc-gateway-paycrypto-me.php:226
msgid "Right — icon after label"
msgstr "Derecha — icono después de la etiqueta"

#: includes/abstract-class-wc-gateway-paycrypto-me.php:234
msgid "Hide for Non-Admin Users"
msgstr "Ocultar para Usuarios No Administradores"

#: includes/abstract-class-wc-gateway-paycrypto-me.php:235
msgid "Show only for administrators."
msgstr "Mostrar solo para administradores."

#: includes/abstract-class-wc-gateway-paycrypto-me.php:238
msgid ""
"If enabled, only administrators will see the payment method on Checkout page."
msgstr ""
"Si está habilitado, solo los administradores verán el método de pago en la "
"página de pago."

#: includes/abstract-class-wc-gateway-paycrypto-me.php:241
msgid "Debug"
msgstr "Depuración"

#: includes/abstract-class-wc-gateway-paycrypto-me.php:242
msgid "Enable debugging messages"
msgstr "Habilitar mensajes de depuración"

#: includes/abstract-class-wc-gateway-paycrypto-me.php:245
msgid "Debug logs will be saved to WooCommerce > Status > Logs."
msgstr ""
"Los registros de depuración se guardarán en WooCommerce > Estado > Registros."

#: includes/abstract-class-wc-gateway-paycrypto-me.php:249
msgid "Support the development!"
msgstr "¡Apoya el desarrollo!"

#: includes/abstract-class-wc-gateway-paycrypto-me.php:255
msgid "<strong>Enjoying the plugin?</strong> Send some BTC to support:"
msgstr ""
"<strong>¿Te está gustando el plugin?</strong> Envía algo de BTC para apoyar:"

